t;;\">in Buckie are </span><span style=\"color: #494949; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">appalling!' <o:p></o:p></span></div>\n<div class=\"Body\" style=\"color: #104100; font-family: TimesNewRomanPSMT; font-size: x-large; font-weight: bold;\">\n<span style=\"color: #494949; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Those </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">near </span><span style=\"color: #494949; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">enough </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">to\nhear her</span><span style=\"color: #6a6a6a; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span><span style=\"color: #494949; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">ye</span><span style=\"color: #202020; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">lp</span><span style=\"color: #494949; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">ed with </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">laughter. There were prison </span><span style=\"color: #494949; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">officers </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">in Eliot's now, their </span><span style=\"color: #494949; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">shifts </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">at the barricades </span><span style=\"color: #494949; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">over. </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Policemen, too. </span><span style=\"color: #494949; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Many of </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">the journalists were </span><span style=\"color: #494949; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">chatting </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">to them</span><span style=\"color: #6a6a6a; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">, </span