span style=\"color: #202020; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">h </span><span style=\"color: #353535; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">lust. <o:p></o:p></span></div>\n<div class=\"Body\" style=\"color: #104100; font-family: TimesNewRomanPSMT; font-size: x-large; font-weight: bold;\">\n<span style=\"color: #6a6a6a; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; '</span><span style=\"color: #353535; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">I'm </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">on your side</span><span style=\"color: #6a6a6a; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">, </span><span style=\"color: #353535; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">darling,’ he </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">shouted. </span><span style=\"color: #6a6a6a; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">'</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">The\nway ah see it—</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">'<span style=\"color: #353535;\"> H</span>e stumbled as he\ntried to move in </span><span style=\"color: #494949; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">on\n</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">her, and much to Rosanna's astonishment,\nAngus </span><span style=\"color: #202020; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">th</span><span style=\"color: #494949; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">en </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">became proprietorial, taking her </span><span style=\"color: #494949; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">roughly by </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">the upper arm.<o:p></o:p></span></div>\n<div class=\"Body\" style=\"color: #104100; font-family: TimesNewRomanPSMT; font-size: x-large; font-weight: bold;\">\n<span style=\"color: #494949; font-family: &quot;Times New Roma